    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade specimen featuring the high-revving S14 inline-four power plant, complete with individual throttle bodies and factory-spec volumetric efficiency. This unit retains its original Getrag 265/5 close-ratio manual gearbox and a 25% locking limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains structurally flawless, exhibiting zero evidence of subframe fatigue or thermal cycling stress on the headers. Suspension kinematics are preserved via refreshed bushings and period-correct dampers, maintaining the precise turn-in characteristics of its homologation roots. The top end has been meticulously indexed, with valve clearances adjusted to factory tolerances. A truly turnkey example for the purist seeking mechanical synchronicity and unparalleled aesthetic preservation.",
